cu.explanation_en: Setting local_s_address to null creates a missing value, causing interface binding failure and preventing proper F1 setup.

du.explanation_en: Changing ssPBCH_BlockPower from integer -25 to string "-25" will cause type validation failure in configuration parsing, leading to system initialization errors.
du.explanation_zh: 將 ssPBCH_BlockPower 從整數 -25 更改為字符串 "-25" 會導致配置解析中的類型驗證失敗，導致系統初始化錯誤。
